title: [NDS] .nfo pack 2801-3500
description:
Self-extracting WinRK archive (http://www.msoftware.co.nz)

All the NFOs from 2801 to 3500 to compliment your rom collection. Grabbed using NdsCRC. 

You may copy this to your NdsCRC cache directory to avoid downloading using the program (can take a really long time). 

*** If you don't trust the .exe, you can still use WinRK to extract the files manually.
